    "title": "When It's Beautiful and Breaking You",
    "subtitle": "Grace for the sacred chaos of motherhood.",
    "category": "mothers",
    "totalDays": 14,
    "description": "Motherhood is holy and exhausting. Fourteen days that meet you in the mess — the doubt, the love, the grace that shows up anyway.",
    "howToUse": null,
